(329697, '2015-07-22 15:41:49', '2015-06-04', 'USD', 'Decomposing fractions', 1118481, 'Khan Academy', 0.0, 'decomposing-fractions,329697/', 'https://www.khanacademy.org/images/khan-logo-vertical-transparent.png', 'https://api.edmodo.com/users/1118481/avatar?type=small&u=dl37i92vt5gab2g7q8gc0l4w7', 'In this tutorial, we''ll see that a fraction can be broken up (or decomposed) into a bunch of other fractions. You might see the world in a completely different way after this.', 0.0, 0),
